item.title: CVE-2020-15235|2024-08-04T13:08:23.234Z -- ractf -- core
item.description: In RACTF before commit f3dc89b, unauthenticated users are able to get the value of sensitive config keys that would normally be hidden to everyone except admins. All versions after commit f3dc89b9f6ab1544a289b3efc06699b13d63e0bd(3/10/20) are patched.
